stock.controller.commands

Class AddToPortfolio

  • java.lang.Object
    • stock.controller.commands.AddToPortfolio
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TradeCommand

    public class AddToPortfolio
extends java.lang.Object
implements TradeCommand
    A class that implements adding stock to portfolio command. The syntax for the command is 'add_stock'. Then based on the strategy command, inputs will be prompted. Any error in parameter asks for re-entry of the parameter. This operation results in stocks being added to the portfolio.
